text: Rueyres-les-Prés was a municipality of the district of Broye in the canton of Fribourg in Switzerland. On 1 January 2017, the former municipalities of Bussy, Estavayer-le-Lac, Morens, Murist, Rueyres-les-Prés, Vernay and Vuissens merged into the new municipality of Estavayer.Historisiertes Gemeindeverzeichnis der Schweiz accessed 5 January 2017 == References == ==Other websites== Category:Former municipalities of Fribourg
title: Rueyres-les-Prés
